div.h1: Ring 3 Ring 0 Transition: Stack Switch via TSS

div.p: CPU detects: Gate DPL CPL Target CS DPL < CPL Privilege escalation required

ol.li: CPU pushes to NEW stack (SS, ESP, EFLAGS, CS, EIP)
CPU loads CS:EIP from IDT gate (kernel handler)

div.p: Total frame: 20 bytes (5 4-byte values) Handler adds: 12-20 bytes more

0x0010FFF0: SS = 0x23 0x0010FFEC: ESP = 0xBFFFF000 0x0010FFE8: EFLAGS 0x0010FFE4: CS = 0x08 0x0010FFE0: EIP = user_eip 0x0010FFDC: EBP (handler pushed) 0x0010FFD8: EBX (handler pushed) 0x0010FFD4: ESI (handler pushed) 0x0010FFD0: EDI (handler pushed)
